Testing Error Log
==================

Permissions-Policy header: Unrecognized feature: 'interest-cohort'

According to Google, FLoC provides a privacy-preserving mechanism for interest-based ad selection.

For example, if you use GitHub Pages or GitLab Pages to host your website, the tag is automatically added to block Google's FLoC technology. {Error can be ignored for MindArt}






